title: U.S. snowboarder Shaun White says his best run is still to come
text:
U.S. snowboarder Shaun White says his best run is still to come Thursday, February 08, 2018 - 01:04 
American Shaun White may have delivered a perfect half-pipe performance to qualify for the Pyeongchang Olympics but the two-time Olympic gold medalist said on Thursday the best was yet to come. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
